snippet.title: R.B.I. Baseball 3 (NES) - Gameplay
snippet.description: It's a rematch of the 1990 All-Star Game in the NES version of R.B.I. Baseball 3. Ryne Sandberg and the NL All-Stars versus Ken Griffey Jr. and the AL All-Stars.
